---
// No Ghost props — copy is entirely hard-coded for this section.
---

<section class="bg-[color:var(--color-fog)]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <p class="font-mono eyebrow text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-[color:var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
      The Process
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-snug text-[color:var(--color-ink)] mb-4 max-w-xl">
      How Does Lawful Access Work?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-base text-[color:var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-12">
      Three simple steps &mdash; all involving a registered Australian practitioner.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 bg-[color:var(--color-white)] rounded-xl px-6 py-8 border border-[color:var(--color-rule)]">
        <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-[color:var(--color-rule)] leading-none" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Register Your Interest</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          Submit your details below. Our team reviews your enquiry.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 bg-[color:var(--color-white)] rounded-xl px-6 py-8 border border-[color:var(--color-rule)]">
        <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-[color:var(--color-rule)] leading-none" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Speak to a Practitioner</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          We connect you with a registered doctor in our network for a clinical consultation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 bg-[color:var(--color-white)] rounded-xl px-6 py-8 border border-[color:var(--color-rule)]">
        <span class="font-serif text-5xl text-[color:var(--color-rule)] leading-none" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">Lawful, Supported Access</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          If suitable, your doctor manages prescribing and supply through regulated channels.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
